					<TextView
						android:id="@+id/story5"
						android:layout_width="match_parent"
						android:layout_height="wrap_content"
						android:layout_marginTop="8dp"
						android:layout_marginBottom="8dp"
						android:padding="8dp"
						android:text="My goodness, I still dey shock till now! I leave my children, Chidera and Kenechukwu, for house, thinking say they go behave themselves small. But when I come back, I see say dem don finish all my milk for fridge! I talk say, &quot;Which kind of wickedness be dis\?&quot;\n\nI ask dem, &quot;Who drink all my milk\?&quot; Dem start to dey look each other, and I know say dem dey plan something. Chidera, my first son, talk say, &quot;Mummy, Kenechukwu drink am.&quot; But Kenechukwu talk say, &quot;No, no, no, Chidera drink am first!&quot;\n\nI shout, &quot;Una dey craze! Who go drink all my milk like dat\?&quot; Dem start to dey cry, and I know say dem dey regret. I tell dem, &quot;Una go drink water for one week, no more milk for una!&quot;\n\nI dey laugh now, but that day, I dey vex. But what can I do\? Dem be my children, and I love dem die. I go buy another milk, and I go make sure say dem no go drink am finish like dat again!"
						android:textSize="12sp"
						android:textColor="#000000"
						android:lines="6" />
